	   <tr><td colspan=2>In groups, pets take NO exp. away from the group. While soloing if you don't outdamage your pet, then it will take 50% of the exp. for the kill. If you do outdamage your pet you get full exp. for the kill.<br><br>Please, try not to unload all of your mana just to outdamage your pet. Its best to aim on doing 55-60% of the damage to a mob yourself, and then let the pet do the rest.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
