	   <tr><td colspan=2>There are two sides to this arguement.<br><br>Erudites have the intelligence and a great spot for 1-5. However their other stats are... lacking<br><br>Dark Elves have a little less intelligence but better stats over all (imho). hunting from 1-5 is ok if you do a little traveling.<br><br>Intelligence is not that hard to raise and faction is not hard either. I would go with Dark Elf. <br><br>However I would suggest you take a serious look at gnomes. Great starting spot. best necro faction?<br><br>Overall race has very little impact on necro playing. I would suggest if you make a necro to take advantage of negative faction and go kill a lot of goodies for exp (bards, rangers, druids come to mind)<br><br>I have a 25 DE necro named Kenven. Feel free to send me a tell sometime if your in need of guidance or wish to add something to the discussion. Or even if you disagree with me. Please rate this post!<br>&nbsp;<br>Slayyer 46 Dark Elf <br>Doldar 33 Human Monk</td></tr>
